    "rationale": "\"Current address\" can be used to measure the regional \"cancer burden\" (cost, medical care needs), especially in major retirement regions. Sometimes central registries carry out follow-up by contacting the patients by a letter or telephone calls to ascertain their vital status. The most current reported address and telephone number are needed. This information is also useful for conducting interview studies.",
    "npcr_collect": "No recommendation",
