    "description": "Codes for the histologic type of the tumor being reported using ICD-O-3. NAACCR adopted ICD-O-3 as the standard coding system for tumors diagnosed in 2001 and later, and recommended that prior tumors be converted from ICD-O-2. Effective with 2010 diagnoses, this item also includes histology codes as per the 2008 WHO Hematopoietic/Lymphoid publication^39^, which are listed on pages 3-5 of the NAACCR 2010 Implementation Guidelines. \\<http://www.naaccr.org/StandardsandRegistryOperations/ImplementationGuidelines.aspx\\>.\r\n\r\nNote: See Histology (92-00) ICD-O-2 \\[420\\] for ICD-O-2 codes. Effective with 2010 diagnoses, this item also includes histology codes as per the 2008 WHO Hematopoietic/Lymphoid publication ^39^, which are listed on pages 3-5 of the NAACCR 2010 Implementation Guidelines. [http://www.naaccr.org/LinkClick.aspx?fileticket=U-3o31G2Lik%3d&tabid=126&mid=466](http://www.naaccr.org/LinkClick.aspx?fileticket=U-3o31G2Lik%3d&tabid=126&mid=466%20)",
    "npcr_collect": "Required",
    "coc_collect": "Required",
    "seer_collect": "Required",
    "cccr_collect": "Required",
    "alternate_names": [
      "ICD-O-3 Histology (CCCR)"
    ],
    "code_note": "**Clarification of Required Status**\r\n\r\nThis data item is required by all standard-setting organizations for tumors diagnosed on or after January 1, 2001, and recommended (by conversion from ICD-O-2 codes when conversion algorithms and tables are available) for tumors diagnosed before 2001.\r\n\r\nWhen the histologic type is coded according to ICD-O-3, the histology code must be reported in Histologic Type ICD-O-3 \\[522\\], with behavior coded in Behavior Code ICD-O-3 \\[523\\].\r\n\r\nFor information on required status for related data items for histologic type and behavior when coded according to ICD-O-2, see Histology (92-00) ICD-O-2 \\[420\\] and Behavior (92-00) ICD-O-2 \\[430\\].",
    "code_description": "See ICD-O-3,^14^ Morphology Section and the SEER Hematopoietic database",
    "allowable_values": "8000-9989, Refer to ICD-O-3"
  },
