    "coc_collect": "No recommendation",
    "seer_collect": "Required",
    "cccr_collect": "No recommendation",
    "code_note": "Historically (before 2010), this was a 1-character field with the following codes in column 19:\r\n\r\n*   1             1992-1994 Version 2 and Version 3\r\n*   4             1995 Version 4.0\r\n*   5             1996 and 1997 Version 5.0 or Version 5.1\r\n*   6             1998 Version 6\r\n*   7             1999 Version 7\r\n*   8             2000 Version 8\r\n*   9             2001 and 2002 Version 9 and 9.1\r\n*   A             2003, 2004, and 2005 Version 10, 10.1, and 10.2\r\n*   B             2006, 2007, and 2008 Version 11, 11.1, 11.2, and 11.3\r\n*   Blank     September 1989 Version\r\n\r\n_Note_: Code 4 was assigned to the 1995 Version to synchronize the document version and the layout version numbers. Layout document Versions 2 and 3 are coded as 1.",
    "allowable_values": "120, 121, 122, 130, 140, 150, 160, 180, 210, 220, 230, 240, 250",
