    "description": "Records an alternate name or “AKA” (also known as) used by the patient, if known. Note that the birth surname (AKA maiden name) is entered in Name--Birth Surname [2232].",
    "general_notes": "*Note*: This data item is no longer supported by CoC (as of January 1, 2003), but is maintained by NAACCR.",
    "rationale": "The update is needed to reflect that Maiden Name is no longer going to be used as of 2021.",
