    "description": "This item indicates the version of Pediatric component of the SEER Staging API used to assign the 2024 and later pediatric staging fields of Pediatric ID and Pediatric input fields. This data item is recorded the first time the Pediatric ID is determined and should be updated each time the related input fields are modified.",
