    "code_note": "Pediatric ID Version Current is a code with up to 2 digits, a decimal and then up to 2 more digits. (e.g., 1.5, 10.12). The first two digits represent the major version number; the second two digits represent minor version changes. The minimum allowable value would be “0.3”. The maximum allowable value would be “99.99”.  Blanks would not be allowed.",
