      "Immunotherapy (SEER/CoC)"
    ],
    "format": "Right justified, zero filled",
    "code_note": "\\*Note :\\*For tumors diagnosed on or after January 1, 2003, information on bone marrow transplants and stem cell transplants should be coded in the new field, RX SUMM--Transplnt/Endocr \\[3250\\]. The CoC standards for hospitals do not allow use of codes 02-06 in tumors diagnosed on or after January 1, 2003.",
    "code_description": "Refer to the most recent version of** **STORE** **and the** **SEER Program Code Manual** **for additional instructions.",
    "allowable_values": "00, 01, 82, 85-88, 99",
    "allowed_codes": [
